sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Browser<br/>(web-app)
    participant API as Identity Core API<br/>(api.fivucsas.com)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>(identity_core)
    participant RD as Redis
    participant SMTP as SMTP relay

    U->>W: fill registration form
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/register<br/>{email, password, firstName, lastName}
    note over W,API: TLS terminated at the Traefik edge.<br/>Bean Validation: e-mail format, password length 8-128

    API->>PG: existsByEmail(email)?

    alt e-mail already registered
        API-->>W: 409 Conflict (duplicate e-mail)
        W-->>U: error message
    else e-mail is new
        API->>API: resolve tenant:<br/>explicit context ><br/>VERIFIED e-mail domain ><br/>legacy domain > default tenant<br/>- else REJECT (fail-closed)
        API->>API: gates: enforce_domain_<br/>matching (V62), tenant<br/>max_users quota
        API->>API: BCrypt hash, cost 12<br/>(deferred until after the gates)
        API->>PG: INSERT user (status = ACTIVE)<br/>DB trigger assigns identity (V70)
        API->>PG: audit log USER_REGISTERED<br/>(+ default member role<br/>if domain-bound)
        API->>RD: store e-mail verification OTP (TTL 5 min)
        API-->>SMTP: send verification code (best-effort)
        API->>PG: INSERT refresh token (rotation family)
        API-->>W: 201 Created<br/>{access JWT RS256, refresh token, user}
        W-->>U: signed in --<br/>e-mail verification pending
    end
